timelineItems.comment: First Half begins.
First Half Extra Time ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Second Half Extra Time begins Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Second Half Extra Time ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Penalty Shootout begins Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Goal!  Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1(1). Agustín Pelletieri (Chivas USA) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the centre of the goal.
Nazmi Albadawi (Carolina RailHawks FC) hits the left post with a right footed shot from the centre of the box.
Goal!  Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1(2). Erick Torres (Chivas USA) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the bottom left corner.
Goal!  Carolina RailHawks FC 1(1), Chivas USA 1(2). Connor Tobin (Carolina RailHawks FC) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the bottom right corner.
Attempt missed. Eriq Zavaleta (Chivas USA) right footed shot from the centre of the box is just a bit too high.
Penalty saved! Kupono Low (Carolina RailHawks FC) fails to capitalise on this great opportunity,  left footed shot saved  in the bottom left corner.
Goal!  Carolina RailHawks FC 1(2), Chivas USA 1(2). Zack Schilawski (Carolina RailHawks FC) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the high centre of the goal.
Attempt saved. Dan Kennedy (Chivas USA) right footed shot from the centre of the box is saved in the bottom left corner.
Attempt saved. Eric Avila (Chivas USA) right footed shot from the centre of the box is saved in the bottom left corner.
Penalty missed! Bad penalty by Enzo Martinez (Carolina RailHawks FC) right footed shot is close, but misses to the right. Enzo Martinez should be disappointed.
Attempt missed. Kristopher Tyrpak (Chivas USA) left footed shot from the centre of the box is just a bit too high.
Penalty saved! Aaron King (Carolina RailHawks FC) fails to capitalise on this great opportunity,  right footed shot saved  in the bottom left corner.
Attempt saved. Marco Delgado (Chivas USA) right footed shot from the centre of the box is saved in the centre of the goal.
Goal!  Carolina RailHawks FC 1(3), Chivas USA 1(2). Daniel Jackson (Carolina RailHawks FC) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the top left corner.
Penalty Shootout ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 1(3), Chivas USA 1(2).
Match ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 1(3), Chivas USA 1(2).
First Half ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Second Half begins Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Second Half ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
First Half Extra Time begins Carolina RailHawks FC 1, Chivas USA 1.
Lineups are announced and players are warming up.
